---
title: Sweet Potato & Spinach Risotto with Toasty Walnuts
description: Get ready for a comforting, fall-inspired risotto! The starchiness of arborio rice gives this classic dish its signature richness and creamy texture. Simmer with sweet potato, garlic, and sage, then stir in leafy green spinach that wilts perfectly. Finish this delicious vegetarian dish with a sprinkle of toasted walnuts for crunchy contrast.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67045d24dcc348117ff3a814-cbcb005a.jpeg
